msgid "Spiritual Seekers and Mystics"
msgstr "Mpikaroka ara-panahy sy Mpifandray"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Curious, introspective, open-minded, and drawn to "
"esoteric knowledge. They may have a strong interest in uncovering hidden "
"meanings or patterns in life. Occupations: Spiritual coaches, tarot readers,"
" astrologers, or individuals involved in New Age practices. Ideological "
"Spectrum: Likely to lean toward spiritual or metaphysical beliefs. They may "
"see the tools as a way to connect with deeper truths or universal energies."
msgstr ""
"Toetra: Kizazaka, mandinika, saina malalaka, ary mankafy fahaiza-manao feno."
" Mety manana fitiavana mafy amin'ny famoahana dika miafina na firafitry ny "
"fiainana. Asa: Mpampianatra ara-panahy, mpamaky tarot, astrologa, na olona "
"miasa amin'ny fanao New Age. Spectrum ideolojika: Mety ho mankaty amin'ny "
"finoana ara-panahy na metaphysika. Mety hanjifany amin'ireo fitaovana ho "
"fomba hifandraisana amin'ny marina lalina na herin'ny tontolo iainana."

msgid "Numerologists and Gematria Enthusiasts"
msgstr "Numerôlôjia sy Mpankafy Gematria"

msgid "Historians and Linguists"
msgstr "Mpanao tantara sy Mpiteny"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Scholarly, methodical, and interested in historical or "
"cultural contexts of numerical systems like Abjad. Occupations: Academics, "
"researchers, or students studying Middle Eastern languages, history, or "
"religious texts. Ideological Spectrum: Likely to approach the tools from a "
"secular, academic perspective, focusing on their historical or linguistic "
"significance."
msgstr ""
"Toetra: Mpanao siansa, manan-drafitra, ary liana amin'ny toe-javatra ara-"
"tantara na kolontsaina amin'ny rafitra isa toy ny Abjad. Asa: Mpampianatra, "
"mpikaroka, na mpianatra mianatra fiteny Azia afovoany, tantara, na soratra "
"ara-pivavahana. Spectrum ideolojika: Mety mihevitra amin'ny fomba "
"siantifika, manampy amin'ny maha-ara-tsaina, manodidina amin'ny maha-azo "
"tsapa amin'ny tantara na teny."

msgid "Religious or Faith-Based Individuals"
msgstr "Olona ara-pivavahana na mifototra amin'ny finoana"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Devout, reflective, and seeking deeper connections to "
"their faith. They may use the tools to explore religious texts or divine "
"messages. Occupations: Religious scholars, imams, priests, or laypeople with"
" a strong interest in their faith’s mystical traditions. Ideological "
"Spectrum: Likely to have a traditional or conservative worldview, using the "
"tools to reinforce their spiritual beliefs."
msgstr ""
"Toetra: Mampanahy, mandinika, ary mitady fifandraisana lalindalina kokoa "
"amin'ny finoany. Mety mampiasa ireo fitaovana mba hijery soratra ara-"
"pivavahana na hafatra masina. Asa: Mpanao fanadihadiana ara-pivavahana, "
"imam, mpangady, na olona mahazatra manana fitiavana amin'ny fomban-drazana "
"amin'ny finoany. Spectrum ideolojika: Mety manana fomba fijery ara-pomba na "
"maharitra, mampiasa ireo fitaovana hanamafisana ny finoany ara-panahy."

msgid "Writers and Artists"
msgstr "Mpanoratra sy Mpanao Sary"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Creative, imaginative, and drawn to symbolic or abstract"
" concepts. They may use the tools for inspiration or to add layers of "
"meaning to their work. Occupations: Authors, poets, visual artists, or "
"musicians. Ideological Spectrum: May range from secular creatives to those "
"with a spiritual or mystical bent."
msgstr ""
"Toetra: Mamorona, feno saina, ary mankafy amin'ny zavatra manan-danja na "
"fanao abstract. Mety mampiasa ireo fitaovana ho famoronana na hanampy "
"laharana amin'ny asany. Asa: Mpandray, poeta, mpanao sary, na mpanao mozika."
" Spectrum ideolojika: Mety miova amin'ny mpamokatra tsy ara-panahy ka "
"hatramin'ny izay manana faniriana ara-panahy na mistery."

msgid "Puzzle and Riddle Enthusiasts"
msgstr "Mpankafy Puzzle sy Riddle"

msgid "Conspiracy Theorists and Alternative Thinkers"
msgstr "Mpanao teori-piadiana sy Mpanao saina hafa"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Skeptical of mainstream narratives, drawn to uncovering "
"hidden truths or patterns in systems. Occupations: Independent researchers, "
"bloggers, or activists. Ideological Spectrum: May have a more radical or "
"unconventional worldview, using the tools to support alternative theories or"
" narratives."
msgstr ""
"Toetra: Mampihena amin'ny tantara mahazatra, mankafy amin'ny fanavahana "
"marina miafina na firafitry amin'ny rafitra. Asa: Mpikaroka misokatra, "
"blogger, na mpandray anjara. Spectrum ideolojika: Mety manana fomba fijery "
"mavesatra na tsy mahazatra, mampiasa ireo fitaovana hanohana teori-piadiana "
"na tantara hafa."

